<item>
            <title>[LU-2923] Enforce the Imperative Recovery requirement of &quot;suppress_pings&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2923</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To reduce the chance of &quot;clients missing server recovery windows&quot; when suppressing pings, we should consider these changes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Check if IR is available and ready before declaring a client is capable of suppressing pings.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Force pings if the MGS is down.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="17789">LU-2923</key>
            <summary>Enforce the Imperative Recovery requirement of &quot;suppress_pings&quot;</summary>
