                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="55824" author="pjones" created="Tue, 9 Apr 2013 05:17:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Landed for 2.4&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="55146" author="liwei" created="Sun, 31 Mar 2013 17:27:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5900&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5900&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is difficult to strictly enforce the IR requirement of &quot;suppress_pings&quot; in the code, given that an MGC does not know if IR is administratively disabled or if a target is mounted with &quot;noir&quot;.  But this patch reduces the chance of the issue during MGS downtimes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
